data.text:
Aster Homes For Sale

Southeast Edmonton

Step into the heart of the Aster Community, one of Edmonton’s newest southeast communities!

Aster offers a wide range of amenities in the area, including a new playground, Costco, Walmart, Superstore, Save-On-Foods, Home Depot, Grey Nuns Hospital, Meadows Medical Clinic, and a sports park. It is also situated near Millwoods Golf Course, Millwoods Recreation Centre, and The Meadows Community Recreation Centre, which features a fitness center, pool, gymnasium, childcare, courts, and more. Regardless of the weather, there is always something to do. This community is ideal for families as there are numerous public and Catholic schools nearby, such as T.D. Baker School, Weinlos School, Father Michael Troy Catholic Junior High School, and Thelma Chalifoux School. Commuting is easy as Aster is close to the Anthony Henday and ETS Meadows Park and Ride, providing easy access to all of Edmonton. Come and discover what this new community has to offer!

If you’re interested in learning more about any of the real estate listings in Aster or anywhere in the Edmonton area, simply click on a property to access all of the details. Additionally, you can sign up for a free account to receive email notifications whenever new listings become available and match your specific home search criteria.
